40:59.820 --> 41:03.153
was beyond your
conscious ability

41:03.190 --> 41:06.227
to control or predict.

41:06.260 --> 41:09.525
- Or negotiate.

41:09.560 --> 41:11.699
- I would suggest

41:11.730 --> 41:13.595
what Will Graham
makes you feel

41:13.630 --> 41:16.861
is not dissimilar.

41:16.900 --> 41:21.007
A force of mind
and Circumstance.

41:21.040 --> 41:22.871
- Love.

41:26.250 --> 41:29.515
He pays you a visit
or he doesn't.

41:29.550 --> 41:32.519
- Same with forgiveness.

41:32.550 --> 41:34.609
And I would argue,

41:34.660 --> 41:37.982
the same with betrayal.

41:38.020 --> 41:41.854
- The god Betrayal. Who
presupposes the god Forgiveness.

41:44.600 --> 41:47.489
- We can all betray.

